%20for%20the%20past%20five%20years%20under%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-losing-safeguard-on-ramp-credit-scores-relief-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epandemic%20pause%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20began%20under%20Trump%20and%20continued%20under%20former%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%20Now%20that%20collections%20have%20restarted%2C%20borrowers%20in%20default%20can%20tap%20into%20three%20different%20options%20to%20evade%20long-term%20consequences%3A%20loan%20rehabilitation%2C%20loan%20consolidation%2C%20or%20bankruptcy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERae%20Kaplan%2C%20a%20student-loan%20attorney%20based%20in%20Chicago%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20while%20default%20consequences%20were%20standard%20before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20the%20five-year%20pause%20brings%20extra%20stress%20to%20the%20collections%20restart%20because%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20people%20took%20this%20out%20of%20their%20budget%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3Bfive%20years%20is%20a%20long%20time%26quot%3B%20to%20get%20used%20to%20not%20paying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I%20think%20this%20period%20where%20they%20start%20ramping%20up%20collection%20activities%20is%20going%20to%20cause%20a%20lot%20of%20panic%20out%20there%20for%20borrowers%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaplan%20said.%20%3Cs%3ESome%20borrowers%20in%20default%20%3C%2Fs%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-react-default-collections-wage-social-security-garnishment-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cs%3Epreviously%20told%20BI%3C%2Fs%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cs%3E%20that%20they're%20not%20confident%20they'll%20be%20able%20to%20avoid%20garnishment.%3C%2Fs%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20options%20that%20defaulted%20student-loan%20borrowers%20have%20to%20avoid%20having%20some%20of%20their%20wages%20and%20federal%20benefits%20seized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d6896dd4-2af8-4965-b5b3-af0db17481ff%5C%22%3ELoan%20rehabilitation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELoan%20rehabilitation%20can%20take%20months%2C%20but%20it%20has%20several%20benefits%2C%20including%20eventual%20removal%20of%20the%20borrower's%20default%20status%20from%20their%20credit%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20rehabilitate%20a%20defaulted%20loan%2C%20the%20borrower%20needs%20to%20contact%20their%20student%20loan%20holder%20and%20sign%20an%20agreement%20to%20make%20nine%20payments%20within%2020%20days%20of%20the%20due%20date%20during%20a%20period%20of%2010%20consecutive%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20payment%20amount%20is%20intended%20to%20be%20affordable%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstudentaid.gov%2Fmanage-loans%2Fdefault%2Fget-out%23loan-rehab%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%2C%20the%20payment%20will%20be%20equal%20to%20up%20to%2015%25%20of%20the%20borrower's%20discretionary%20income%20divided%20by%2012.%20Kaplan%20said%20that%20it's%20helpful%20to%20hire%20an%20attorney%20or%20an%20advocate%20to%20negotiate%20low%20payments%2C%20and%20it's%20possible%20that%20borrowers%20can%20end%20up%20with%20payments%20as%20low%20as%20%245%20a%20month%20through%20this%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20wage%20and%20benefits%20garnishment%20will%20continue%20during%20part%20of%20the%20loan%20rehabilitation%20process%2C%20and%20the%20benefits%20that%20are%20seized%20would%20be%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20agreed-upon%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Erehabilitation%20payments.%20Garnishment%20will%20continue%20until%20the%20borrower%20has%20made%20at%20least%20five%20rehabilitation%20payments%20or%20the%20loan%20is%20no%20longer%20in%20default.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20borrowers%20can%20only%20rehabilitate%20a%20defaulted%20student%20loan%20once%3B%20if%20the%20loan%20defaults%20again%2C%20rehabilitation%20will%20not%20be%20an%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20we%20get%20you%20rehabilitated%2C%20then%20your%20credit%20score%20will%20go%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Kaplan%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20a%20nice%20feature%20that%20you%20can%20both%20get%20back%20to%20current%20and%20in%20good%20standing%2C%20get%20your%20loans%20back%20into%20good%20status%2C%20and%20get%20that%20negative%20credit%20removed%20from%20your%20credit%20report.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fcd1f6e8-dcca-4ff6-92af-c58b21d72ef8%5C%22%3ELoan%20consolidation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EConsolidating%20a%20defaulted%20student%20loan%20is%20quicker%20than%20rehabilitation%2C%20but%20the%20record%20of%20the%20default%20will%20remain%20on%20the%20borrower's%20credit%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowers%20can%20apply%20with%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20consolidate%20their%20defaulted%20student%20loans%20into%20a%20federal%20direct%20consolidation%20loan.%20To%20be%20approved%20for%20consolidation%2C%20the%20borrower%20must%20agree%20to%20pay%20off%20the%20consolidated%20loan%20under%20an%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan%20or%20make%20three%20consecutive%2C%20on-time%2C%20full%20monthly%20payments%20before%20consolidating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20loan%20is%20consolidated%2C%20the%20borrower%20can%20make%20use%20of%20all%20federal%20student-loan%20benefits%2C%20including%20deferments%2C%20forbearances%2C%20and%20loan%20forgiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225bf9acc0-8565-412d-9886-9aa24cb6facd%5C%22%3EBankruptcy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20defaulted%20borrower%20does%20not%20think%20that%20consolidation%20or%20rehabilitation%20is%20feasible%2C%20they%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-discharge-student-loans-in-bankruptcy-boomer-debt-relief-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efile%20for%20bankruptcy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDustin%20Baker%2C%20an%20Iowa%20bankruptcy%20attorney%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20filing%20for%20bankruptcy%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%20efficient%20way%26quot%3B%20to%20stop%20wage%20and%20benefits%20garnishment%20because%20once%20a%20bankruptcy%20petition%20is%20filed%2C%20creditors%20are%20no%20longer%20allowed%20to%20contact%20and%20collect%20from%20the%20borrower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20nothing%20else%2C%20it's%20kind%20of%20a%20four%20or%20five-month%20break%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Baker%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he's%20already%20received%20an%20increase%20in%20requests%20from%20borrowers%20worried%20about%20collections%20on%20defaulted%20student%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%202022%2C%20student-loan%20borrowers%20had%20to%20clear%20a%20high%20and%20burdensome%20threshold%20to%20discharge%20their%20loans%20in%20bankruptcy.%20However%2C%20Biden%20issued%20new%20guidance%20in%20November%202022%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-get-new-path-to-discharge-debt-bankruptcy-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estreamline%20the%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Baker%20said%20he's%20had%20much%20greater%20success%20discharging%20borrowers'%20student%20loans%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20like%20it's%20moving%20more%20quickly%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Baker%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey've%20allocated%20the%20appropriate%20resources%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20a%20partisan%20thing.%20Biden%20started%20this%20process%2C%20Trump%20reaffirmed%20it%2C%20and%20it%20sounds%20like%20the%20administration%20at%20least%20is%20providing%20the%20appropriate%20resources%20to%20make%20it%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-defaulted-student-loan-borrowers-avoid-wage-social-security-garnishment-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747466821000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654cfc29b788914e55533bf0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-defaulted-student-loan-borrowers-avoid-wage-social-security-garnishm