lder%20workers%3B%20and%20claims%20from%20Mulholland%20of%20a%20concealed%20romantic%20relationship%20between%20Mah%20and%20former%20Google%20CEO%20Eric%20Schmidt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMah%2C%20who%20says%20she%20has%20been%20programming%20since%20middle%20school%2C%20was%20featured%20on%20Forbes'%20%26quot%3B30%20under%2030%26quot%3B%20list%20in%202012%20and%20was%20on%20the%20front%20page%20of%20Inc%20magazine%20in%202015.%20She%20founded%20inDinero%2C%20a%20fintech%20startup%20that%20created%20a%20financial%20dashboard%20for%20businesses%2C%20and%20then%20her%20VC%20firm%20called%20Mahway%2C%20which%20she%20has%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bventure%20builder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECaldbeck%2C%20who%20also%20worked%20at%20Bain%20Capital%20Ventures%20and%20Lightspeed%20Ventures%2C%20resigned%20from%20the%20fund%20he%20founded%2C%20Binary%20Capital%2C%20in%202017%20after%20a%20group%20of%20women%20shared%20accusations%20of%20sexual%20harassment.%20Caldbeck%20admitted%20to%20his%20inappropriate%20behavior%20toward%20female%20founders%20and%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20Friday%2C%20Mah%20said%20she%20had%20spent%20months%20trying%20to%20resolve%20the%20dispute%20with%20Caldbeck%20privately%20before%20filing%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20recognize%20the%20risks%20and%20backlash%20that%20may%20follow%2C%20and%20I've%20made%20peace%20with%20the%20consequences%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20step%20I%20take%20lightly.%20I%20believe%20in%20doing%20business%20with%20transparency%2C%20accountability%2C%20and%20clarity%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20will%20always%20stand%20up%20for%20those%20values%2C%20regardless%20of%20how%20uncomfortable%20it%20may%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20emailed%20statement%2C%20Caldbeck%20spokesperson%20Sallie%20Hofmeister%20denied%20the%20claims%20of%20sexual%20misconduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Caldbeck%20never%20made%20sexual%20advances%20toward%20Ms.%20Mah%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20complaint%2C%20Mah%20alleges%20that%20Caldbeck%20sexually%20harassed%20her%20in%202022.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20consuming%20several%20drinks%20during%20a%20business%20meeting%20at%20the%20restaurant%20at%20the%20Pendry%20Hotel%20in%20West%20Hollywood%2C%20California%2C%20Mr.%20Caldbeck%20touched%20the%20upper-most%20part%20of%20Ms.%20Mah's%20thigh%20and%20put%20his%20hand%20next%20to%20her%20genitalia%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20says.%20It%20goes%20on%20to%20allege%20that%20Caldbeck%20repeatedly%20asked%20Mah%20if%20she%20was%20sexually%20interested%20in%20him%20and%20discussed%20his%20sexual%20relationships%20with%20other%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMah%20alleges%20in%20the%20suit%20that%20Caldbeck%20misled%20his%20own%20investors%20about%20the%20nature%20of%20his%20investment%20in%20one%20of%20her%20entities%2C%20and%20then%20%26quot%3Bscreamed%20at%20her%20and%20demanded%20she%20immediately%20pay%20him%20three%20times%20his%20initial%20investment.%26quot%3B%20When%20she%20refused%2C%20the%20suit%20says%2C%20he%20told%20her%20that%20%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20destroy%20you%26quot%3B%20and%20defamed%20her%20to%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20complaint%20alleges%20extortion%2C%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20and%20defamation%2C%20among%20other%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20cases%20against%20Mah%2C%20filed%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20Superior%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20Thursday%20by%20San%20Francisco-based%20law%20firm%20Sawyer%20%26amp%3B%20Labar%20LLC%2C%20accuse%20her%20of%20improperly%20using%20company%20funds%20to%20pay%20for%20her%20personal%20life.%20The%20claims%20variously%20include%20leasing%20a%20Lamborghini%2C%20vacation%20trips%20to%20Burning%20Man%20and%20Park%20City%2C%20covering%20rent%20for%20her%20home%2C%20paying%20for%20personal%20chefs%20and%20landscaping%20services%2C%20and%20paying%20for%20a%20personal%20jet%20despite%20employees'%20objections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHofmeister%2C%20also%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Mulholland%20and%20Delph%2C%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20their%20lawsuits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMah%20is%20more%20interested%20in%20living%20an%20ersatz%20glamorous%20lifestyle%20than%20investing%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DGV%20complaint%20read.%20%26quot%3BThe%20result%20of%20Mah's%20dereliction%20of%20duty%20was%20predictable%20for%20the%20Company%20and%20its%20investors%3A%20investments%20were%20not%20as%20fruitful%2C%20making%20no%20real%20progress%2C%20while%20Mah%20seduced%20investors%20with%20misleading%20and%20often%20contradictory%20representations%20in%20quarterly%20investor%20reports.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelph's%20complaint%20alleges%20that%20workers%20were%20required%20to%20work%20from%20Mah's%20home%2C%20and%20that%20her%20friends%20and%20sexual%20partners%20would%20visit%20during%20the%20workday%20and%20walk%20around%20%26quot%3Bin%20various%20stages%20of%20undress.%26quot%3B%20Mah%20would%20talk%20about%20sexual%20encounters%20with%20her%20employees%2C%20amounting%20to%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20the%20suit%20says.%20Delph%20also%20alleges%20that%20Mah%20called%20him%20an%20%26quot%3Bold%20man%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bridiculed%26quot%3B%20him%20because%20of%20his%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMulholland's%20complaint%20alleges%20that%20an%20investor%20in%20Mahway%20complained%20that%20Mah%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bconcealing%20her%20former%20sexual%20relationship%20with%20Eric%20Schmidt%2C%20the%20largest%20Mahway%20investor%20and%20former%20CEO%20of%20Google%2C%20in%20order%20to%20make%20Mahway%20appear%20like%20a%20legitimate%20investment%20opportunity.%26quot%3B%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20Schmidt%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20purported%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDGV's%20complaint%20claims%20that%20Mah%20%26quot%3Bmisled%26quot%3B%20the%20firm%20into%20falsely%20believing%20that%20Schmidt's%20family%20office%20had%20invested%20in%20Mahway.%20However%2C%20Schmidt's%20spokesperson%20said%20this%20is%20false%2C%20and%20that%20Schmidt%20was%20indeed%20an%20investor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelph%20claims%20to%20have%20been%20fired%20after%20raising%20concerns%20to%20Mah%20internally%20at%20a%20management%20meeting%2C%20while%20Mulholland's%20suit%20says%20he%20felt%20forced%20to%20resign%20because%20Mah%20%26quot%3Bwas%20ordering%20him%20to%20break%20the%20law%20by%20concealing%20and%2For%20misrepresenting%20material%20facts%20while%20engaging%20in%20general%20solicitation%20of%20investors%20in%20an%20unregistered%20security.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20claims%20in%20Delph's%20complaint%20include%20whistleblower%20retaliation%2C%20wrongful%20termination%2C%20age%20discrimination%20and%20sexual%20harassment.%20Mulholland%20claims%20constructive%20discharge%20and%20whistleblower%20retaliation%2C%20among%20other%20claims.%20And%20DGV's%20claims%20include%20breach%20of%20fiduciary%20duty%2C%20breach%20of%20contract%2C%20civil%20theft%2C%20and%20sale%20of%20unregistered%20securities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAdditional%20reporting%20by%20Jack%20Newsham.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EGot%20a%20story%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20Contact%20reporter%20Rob%20Price%20via%20Signal%20at%20%2B1%20650-636-6268%20or%20email%20at%20rprice%40insider.com.%20Use%20a%20non-work%20device%20to%20reach%20out.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjessica-mah-justin-caldbeck-ex-mahway-employees-legal-disputes-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1747452975000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6827f0663fe8d39283662763%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjessica-mah-justin-caldbeck-ex-mahway-employees-legal-disputes-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jessica%20Mah%20accuses%20Justin%20Caldbeck%20of%20sexual%20harassment.%20She%20is%20accused%20of%20financial%20impropriety%2C%20harassment%2C%20and%20discrimination.%22%2C%22au