20AI-powered%20recruitment%20tools%20which%20are%20often%20%26quot%3Bwrappers%20around%20the%20same%20core%20models%20or%20APIs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20them%20may%20not%20use%20the%20latest%20or%20most%20stable%20versions%2C%20which%20could%20explain%20why%20similar%20glitches%20show%20up%20across%20platforms%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnaizah%20Obaidellah%2C%20a%20senior%20lecturer%20specializing%20in%20AI%20at%20Malaysia's%20University%20of%20Malaya%2C%20said%20insufficient%20or%20irrelevant%20data%20could%20also%20be%20a%20culprit.%20If%20the%20bots%20are%20not%20trained%20with%20enough%20relevant%20examples%2C%20their%20quality%20suffers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20the%20incidents%20portrayed%20on%20the%20videos%20could%20reflect%20the%20larger%20race%20to%20deploy%20AI%20faster%20than%20we're%20ready%20for%2C%20which%20is%20%26quot%3Bquite%20worrying.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dcf20482-f547-4752-8b45-28b9b0d852e9%5C%22%3EAI%20interviews%20on%20the%20rise%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEmily%20DeJeu%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20at%20Carnegie%20Mellon%20University's%20Tepper%20School%20of%20Business%20who%20specializes%20in%20AI%20communication%20and%20etiquette%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-interviews-ai-robots-how-to-prepare-keywords-advice-recruitment-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBI%20earlier%20this%20week%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20AI-powered%20video%20interviews%20are%20likely%20to%20become%20more%20common%20as%20companies%20seek%20to%20streamline%20and%20automate%20early%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjob-ads-too-long-requirements-algorithm-rejecting-applications-frustration-recruitment-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehiring%20stages%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20time%20technology%20promises%20to%20save%20time%20and%20money%20and%20make%20everything%20faster%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20by%20default%20pursue%20it%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20a%20kind%20of%20inevitability%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20what%20the%20TikToks%20might%20suggest%2C%20candidates%20aren't%20necessarily%20turned%20off%20by%20bots%2C%20said%20Iyer%2C%20who%20has%20worked%20in%20HR%20tech%20for%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f9cafe56-6c95-4138-9a59-e2d88f768adc%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20do%20if%20your%20interview%20bot%20glitches%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGlitches%20during%20AI%20interviews%20aren't%20just%20awkward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGlitches%20chip%20away%20at%20trust%20and%20can%20make%20the%20hiring%20process%20feel%20impersonal%20or%20even%20unfair%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tan%2C%20especially%20if%20companies%20are%20not%20upfront%20about%20conducting%20an%20AI%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20undermine%20the%20candidate's%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20employers%20need%20to%20%26quot%3Bbuild%20in%20strong%20fallback%20options%26quot%3B%20and%20monitor%20these%20tools%20closely%20in%20real-world%20settings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOtherwise%2C%20what%20feels%20like%20a%20time-saving%20solution%20could%20quietly%20become%20a%20systemic%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20candidates%2C%20the%20key%20is%20not%20to%20panic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20an%20AI%20bot%20malfunctions%20mid-interview%2C%20Tan%20recommends%20emailing%20the%20hiring%20manager%20with%20a%20screenshot%20or%20recording%20of%20what%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20should%20offer%20a%20redo%20assuming%20the%20candidate%20isn't%20already%20put%20off%20by%20the%20idea%20of%20being%20interviewed%20by%20a%20bot%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnaizah%2C%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Malaya%2C%20said%20candidates%20can%20also%20request%20feedback%20from%20the%20HR%20team%20on%20their%20interview%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20there's%20clear%20evidence%20the%20interview%20wasn't%20properly%20assessed%20%E2%8