0href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteen-wins-isef-science-fair-grand-prize-discovery-biomedical-devices-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einternational%20science%20competition%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20did%20not%20expect%20to%20come%20home%20with%20%24100%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2019-year-old%20from%20Dulovce%2C%20Slovakia%20won%20that%20sum%20on%20Friday%2C%20though%2C%20because%20he%20developed%20a%20faster%20and%20cheaper%20way%20to%20make%20an%20experimental%20antiviral%20drug%20called%20galidesivir%2C%20which%20targets%20RNA%20viruses%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmetformin-diabetes-weight-loss-anti-aging-drug-long-covid-prevention-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECOVID-19%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ebola%2C%20and%20Zika%20virus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20could%20be%20a%20huge%20step%20to%20help%20prevent%20some%20of%20these%20RNA%20viruses%2C%26quot%3B%20Chris%20RoDee%2C%20a%20chemist%20and%20retired%20patent%20examiner%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20studies%20have%20shown%20galidesivir%20can%20attack%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrna-vaccine-pfizer-moderna-coronavirus-2020-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERNA%20viruses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it%20has%20not%20undergone%20full%20clinical%20trials.%20Koval%C4%8D%C3%ADk%20thinks%20he%20can%20encourage%20further%20research%20by%20slashing%20the%20cost%20of%20producing%20the%20drug%20%E2%80%94%20from%20%2475%20per%20gram%20to%20about%20%2412.50%20per%20gram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20he%20used%20corn%20waste%20to%20synthesize%20twice%20as%20much%20of%20the%20drug%20in%20just%2010%20steps%2C%20rather%20than%20the%2015%20steps%20currently%20required%20for%20manufacturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKoval%C4%8D%C3%ADk%20even%20went%20one%20step%20further%3A%20He%20used%20his%20method%20to%20make%20a%20new%20drug%20that%20could%20also%20fight%20RNA%20viruses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKoval%C4%8D%C3%ADk%20presente