0it%20could%20be%20tricky%20to%20place%20some%20soundbars%20in%20front.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Murphy%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESetting%20the%20C4%20up%20is%20a%20pretty%20simple%20process%20%E2%80%94%20just%20four%20screws%20to%20attach%20its%20stand%2C%20though%20you'll%20need%20a%20friend%20to%20help%20you%20lug%20it%20into%20place%20if%20your%20screen%20is%2055%20inches%20or%20larger.%20However%2C%20the%20stand%20only%20raises%20the%20TV%20around%202.25%20inches%2C%20which%20could%20be%20an%20issue%20if%20you%20own%20a%20large%20soundbar%2C%20and%20its%20pedestal%20design%20means%20you'll%20need%20to%20place%20your%20soundbar%20directly%20in%20front%20of%20the%20stand%20rather%20than%20right%20underneath%20the%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20booted%20up%2C%20the%20TV%20guides%20you%20through%20some%20standard%20housekeeping%20tasks%20like%20setting%20up%20WiFi%20and%20accepting%20various%20terms%20and%20services.%20The%20C4%20supports%20Ethernet%20(via%20one%20port%20on%20the%20side)%20and%20WiFi%205%2C%20which%20is%20on%20the%20slower%20side%20for%20a%20modern%20TV.%20You'll%20mainly%20feel%20that%20when%20your%20set%20is%20downloading%20larger%20software%20and%20app%20updates%2C%20but%20you%20shouldn't%20have%20any%20issues%20streaming%204K%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20all%20modern%20TVs%2C%20the%20set%20also%20has%20a%20digital%20over-the-air%20(OTA)%20tuner%20port%2C%20which%20is%20great%20if%20you%C2%A0want%20to%20plug%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-hdtv-indoor-antenna%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eantenna%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20access%20free%2C%20local%20signals%20without%20paying%20a%20fortune%20to%20a%20cable%20provider.%20That%20said%2C%20the%20C4's%20tuner%20only%20supports%20receiving%20HD%20broadcasts%20rather%20than%204K%20Ultra%20HD.%20This%20isn't%20a%20big%20deal%20since%20the%20majority%20of%20OTA%20content%20is%20limited%20to%20HD%20in%20most%20areas.%20You%20can%20also%20buy%20a%204K%20tuner%20separately%20if%20you%20ever%20want%20to%20upgrade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20C4%20has%20plenty%20of%20ports%20for%20connecting%20external%20devices%20like%20a%20streaming%20player%2C%20AV%20receiver%2C%20soundbar%2C%20or%20gaming%20console.%20The%20set%20has%20four%20HDMI%202.1%20inputs%20with%20support%20for%2048Gbps%2C%20enabling%20the%20bandwidth%20needed%20for%204K%2F120Hz%20signals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20the%20LG%20C4%20TV's%20side%20HDMI%20and%20antenna%20ports.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68277754c6ad288d14812e6d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221406%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20TV%20has%20multiple%20HDMI%20inputs%20as%20well%20as%20an%20antenna%20port.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Murphy%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESetting%20up%20the%20C4's%20built-in%20Universal%20Control%20feature%2C%20a%20fancy%20way%20of%20saying%20%26quot%3Buse%20one%20remote%20to%20control%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20requires%20almost%20no%20effort%20at%20all.%20I%20just%20had%20to%20pick%20my%20connected%20AV%20receiver's%20manufacturer%20and%20run%20through%20a%20quick%20test%20of%20the%20power%20button.%20Coupled%20with%20the%20HDMI-CEC%20capabilities%2C%20I%20could%20then%20use%20the%20Magic%20Remote's%20buttons%20to%20raise%20and%20lower%20my%20receiver's%20volume%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20many%20options%20on%20its%20setup%20screen.%20Though%20not%20as%20full-featured%20as%20a%20true%20universal%20remote%2C%20it's%20still%20super-convenient%20for%20basic%20operations%20across%20many%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20summon%20LG's%20digital%20assistant%20by%20saying%20%26quot%3BHi%2C%20LG%26quot%3B%20to%20your%20TV%2C%20once%20you've%20set%20it%20up%2C%20or%20by%20holding%20down%20the%20associated%20button%20on%20LG's%20Magic%20Remote.%20It's%20surprisingly%20good%2C%20able%20to%20launch%20apps%2C%20jump%20to%20different%20networks%20within%20LG's%20Channels%20app%2C%20and%20even%20pull%20up%20your%20settings%20whenever%20you%20want%20(in%20addition%20to%20telling%20you%20the%20weather).%20I%20was%20actually%20surprised%20by%20the%20voice%20assistant's%20versatility%2C%20and%20frequently%20found%20myself%20talking%20to%20the%20TV%20to%20power%20it%20up%20whenever%20I%20walked%20into%20the%20living%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELG%20also%20offers%20the%20option%20to%20set%20up%20several%20AI-powered%20modes%20to%20automatically%20adjust%20the%20brightness%20of%20scenes%2C%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20TV's%20speakers%2C%20and%2C%20as%20far%20as%20I%20can%20tell%2C%20upscale%20lower-resolution%20video%20for%20the%20TV's%204K%20screen.%20None%20of%20the%20visual%20features%20had%20any%20noticeable%20impact%20on%20my%20testing%20when%20enabled.%20I%20repeatedly%20turned%20them%20on%20and%20off%20during%20a%20variety%20of%20movies%2C%20and%20their%20%26quot%3Bbenefits%26quot%3B%20were%20minimal%2C%20at%20best.%20My%20advice%3F%20You%20don't%20need%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20single%20AI%20audio%20enhancement%20option%20seemed%20to%20normalize%20the%20TV's%20volume%20and%20make%20everything%20sound%20equal%20and%20annoyingly%20louder%2C%20removing%20all%20the%20acoustic%20joy%20from%20scenes%20like%20the%20big%20spice%20harvester%20attack%20in%20%26quot%3BDune%3A%20Part%20Two.%26quot%3B%20The%20TV's%20calibration-like%20AI%20Acoustic%20Tuning%20didn't%20give%20me%20noticeably%20different%20audio%20quality%20when%20on%20or%20off%2C%20save%20for%20when%20I%20switched%20the%20feature%20to%20bass-%20or%20treble-boosting%20mode.%20Again%2C%20the%20LG%20C4%20performs%20better%20without%20these%20additions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a6d5743e-c68c-4781-ad74-2cc68e713d1a%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Picture%20performance%5C%22%3EThe%20C4%20has%20great%20picture%20quality%2C%20as%20long%20as%20you%20use%20the%20right%20settings%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221773%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20LG%20C4%20OLED%20TV%20is%20displaying%20a%20demo%20video%20of%20two%20skydivers%20in%20the%20air.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6827779f3fe8d392836618b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221330%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20C4's%20contrast%20performance%20is%20exceptional%2C%20and%20its%20Cinema%20and%20Filmmaker%20modes%20offer%20an%20accurate%20image.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Murphy%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELG's%20C4%20uses%20a%20WOLED%20panel%2C%20giving%20you%20pixel-perfect%20dimming%20that%20doesn't%20create%20any%20annoying%20halos%20or%20other%20artifacts%20when%20bright%20images%20are%20blasted%20across%20an%20otherwise%20dark%20scene%20%E2%80%94%20a%20fireball%20on%20an%20Arrakis%20night%20in%20%26quot%3BDune%2C%26quot%3B%20for%20example.%20This%20instantly%20gives%20the%20C4%20a%20leg%20up%20on%20competing%20QLED%20TVs%20that%20rely%20on%20backlights%20arranged%20into%20zones%20to%20control%20the%20brightness%20of%20various%20parts%20of%20your%20picture.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20contrast%2C%20OLED%20is%20simply%20superior%2C%20full%20stop.%20The%20C4's%20OLED%20screen%20also%20offers%20wider%20viewing%20angles%20than%20a%20QLED%2C%20though%20some%20slight%20shifts%20in%20color%20tint%20can%20be%20visible.%20Visit%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fqled-vs-oled%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EQLED%20vs.%20OLED%20comparison%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20details%20on%20the%20pros%20and%20cons%20of%20both%20display%20types.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20C4%20does%20stop%20short%20of%20using%20the%20more%20advanced%20panel%20that%20LG%20uses%20on%20its%20pricier%20G%20Series%20OLED%20TVs.%20Samsung%20and%20Sony%20also%20use%20more%20advanced%20OLED%20screens%20that%20incorporate%20quantum%20dots%20in%20their%20flagship%20sets.%20In%20practice%2C%20this%20means%20the%20C4%20can't%20get%20quite%20as%20bright%20or%20colorful%20as%20those%20models%2C%20but%20the%20TV%20still%20performs%20well%20for%20its%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20evaluated%20the%20C4's%20image%20quality%20by%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.portrait.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPortrait%20Displays'%20Calman%20software%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20measure%20every%20one%20of%20the%20TV's%20video%20presets%20across%20both%20SDR%20and%20HDR.%20The%20TV's%20default%20%26quot%3BStandard%26quot%3B%20preset%20is%20not%20very%20good.%20That's%20to%20be%20expected%20on%20most%20TVs%2C%20but%20its%20inaccuracies%20in%20both%20grayscales%20and%20colors%20were%20bigger%20than%20anything%20I've%20seen%20in%20some%20time.%20Even%20before%20I%20busted%20out%20my%20colorimeter%2C%20something%20about%20the%20TV's%20default%20image%20seemed%20way%20too%20blue%20and%20cool-toned.%20My%20tests%20completely%20confirmed%20that%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20some.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20this%20is%20easily%20corrected%20by%20switching%20to%20one%20of%20the%20TV's%20much%20more%20accurate%20presets.%20If%20you%20switch%20to%20Filmmaker%2C%20ISF%20Expert%2C%20or%20Cinema%20mode%2C%20it's%20like%20you're%20looking%20at%20a%20completely%20different%20set.%20I%20expected%20the%20Filmmaker%20or%20ISF%20Expert%20modes%20to%20have%20the%20best%20picture%20quality%2C%20given%20that%20they%20tend%20to%20minimize%20any%20kind%20of%20unnecessary%20processing%2C%20but%20the%20TV's%20Cinema%20mode%20was%20actually%20the%20most%20accurate%20for%20grayscale%20and%20colors.%20Filmmaker%20and%20ISF%20Expert%20(both%20its%20%26quot%3Blight%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdark%20space%26quot%3B%20modes)%20were%20still%20great%2C%20and%20I'd%20be%20fine%20using%20any%20of%20the%20three%20if%20one%20happened%20to%20catch%20my%20eye%20more%20than%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TV's%20HDR%20(high%20dynamic%20range)%20mode%20provides%20more%20presets%20to%20pick%20from%2C%20and%20again%2C%20I%20highly%20recommend%20ignoring%20the%20Standard%20and%20Vivid%20presets%20in%20favor%20of%20Filmmaker%20or%20Cinema%20modes.%20Cinema%20was%20again%20the%20preset%20to%20beat%2C%20delivering%20grayscale%20and%20color%20errors%20so%20low%20that%20they're%20not%20perceptible%20to%20the%20eye.%20Switching%20to%20it%20also%20automatically%20turns%20off%20the%20TV's%20terrible%20TruMotion%20option%2C%20a%20motion-smoothing%20feature%20that%20makes%20all%20your%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows%20look%20like%20they%20were%20shot%20as%20soap%20operas.%20Gross.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221773%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20angled%20view%20of%20an%20LG%20C4%20OLED%20displaying%20a%20video%20of%20a%20car%20driving%20across%20a%20bridge.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6827781fc6ad288d14812e99%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221330%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20C4's%20brightness%20is%20solid%20for%20a%20midrange%20OLED%2C%20and%20it%20has%20great%20viewing%20angles.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Murphy%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20brightness%2C%20the%20C4%20performs%20well%20for%20a%20midrange%20OLED%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20at%20the%20top%20of%20its%20class.%20Using%2010%25%20windows%2C%20I%20measured%20a%20maximum%20brightness%20of%20355.3%20nits%20and%20998.6%20nits%20on%20the%20TV's%20Cinema%20mode%20for%20SDR%20and%20HDR%2C%20respectively.%20For%20comparison%2C%20LG's%20new%20C5%20can%20get%20slightly%20brighter%20at%201%2C174%20nits%20in%20HDR%2C%20and%20Samsung's%20similarly%20priced%20S90D%20can%20get%20hit%20around%201%2C200%20nits%20in%20HDR.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20brightest%20OLED%20available%20right%20now%2C%20LG's%20high-end%20G5%2C%20can%20hit%202%2C400%20nits%20in%20HDR.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHigher%20luminance%20helps%20high-contrast%20scenes%20pop%20with%20more%20intensity%2C%20like%20the%20extended%20infrared%20fighting%20sequence%20in%20%26quot%3BDune%3A%20Part%20Two.%26quot%3B%20That%20said%2C%20I%20wasn't%20bothered%20by%20any%20brightness%20issues%20when%20watching%20most%20HDR%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows.%20A%20lot%20of%20HDR%20content%20is%20mastered%20for%20a%20max%20of%201%2C000%20nits%2C%20so%20the%20C4%20presents%20that%20material%20without%20any%20issues.%20As%20you'd%20expect%2C%20super-dark%20moments%20in%20scenes%20blended%20right%20into%20a%20movie's%20black%20letterboxing%20%E2%80%94%20the%20power%20of%20OLED%20%E2%80%94%20and%20movies%20like%20%26quot%3BTron%3A%20Legacy%26quot%3B%20had%20a%20pleasing%2C%20cyberpunk%20glow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudios%20do%20master%20some%20HDR%20content%20for%20higher%20brightness%20levels%20that%20max%20out%20at%202%2C000%2C%204%2C000%2C%20and%20even%2010%2C000%20nits%2C%20so%20the%20C4%20does%20fall%20short%20when%20displaying%20that%20kind%20of%20material.%20If%20you%20had%20a%20C4%20side-by-side%20with%20an%20OLED%20that%20can%20hit%201%2C500%2B%20nits%2C%20you%20would%20see%20specular%20highlights%20(like%20explosions%20or%20shimmering%20reflections)%20look%20more%20impactful%20on%20the%20other%20TV.%20In%20that%20sense%2C%20big%20home%20theater%20enthusiasts%20should%20consider%20paying%20top%20dollar%20for%20an%20LG%20G%20Series%20OLED.%20But%20I'd%20only%20be%20annoyed%20by%20the%20C4's%20limitations%20if%20LG%20was%20positioning%20it%20as%20a%20top-shelf%20TV.%20For%20its%20price%2C%20the%20C4%20wows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20TV%20is%20also%20well-equipped%20for%20gaming%20on%20current-gen%20consoles.%20The%20set's%20native%20refresh%20rate%20of%20120Hz%20is%20a%20pretty%20standard%20inclusion%20nowadays.%20This%20can%20go%20up%20to%20144Hz%20when%20you've%20connected%20a%20compatible%20gaming%20PC%2C%20and%20it%20can%20use%20Nvidia%20G-Sync%20or%20AMD%20FreeSync%20Premium%20to%20dynamically%20adjust%20the%20refresh%20rates%20during%20gameplay%20to%20give%20you%20a%20buttery-smooth%20picture.%20(Only%20a%20few%20TVs%2C%20like%20LG's%20G5%2C%20go%20any%20higher%2C%20supporting%20a%20maximum%20gaming%20refresh%20rate%20of%20165Hz.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20class%2C%20the%20C4's%20biggest%20competitor%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15109636506tul-20%26h%3Df345fe01195470e00dd2d1c3fca548c2ccf62c8056e1550218b2498caa0155ec%26postID%3D68273af5a865711b0ac0e160%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Flg-c4-oled-4k-tv-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FSAMSUNG-Tracking-Xcelerator-Enhancer-Upscaling%252Fdp%252FB0CV9VGMPT%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESamsung%20S90D%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%2055-%2C%2065-%2C%20and%2077-inch%20S90D%20TVs%20integrate%20quantum%20dots%20into%20their%20OLED%20screens%2C%20giving%20them%20slightly%20brighter%20performance%20with%20higher%20color%20volume.%20However%2C%20the%2042-%2C%2048-%2C%20and%2083-inch%20models%20don't%20have%20quantum%20dots%2C%20so%20they%20don't%20offer%20any%20big%20picture%20benefits%20over%20the%20C4.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20worth%20mentioning%20that%20the%20S90D%20doesn't%20support%20Dolby%20Vision%2C%20while%20the%20C4%20does.%20Dolby%20Vision%20isn't%20a%20must-have%20feature%2C%20but%20it%20is%20a%20nice%20perk.%20Dolby%20Vision%20is%20supported%20by%20many%20streaming%20apps%20and%204K%20Blu-ray%20discs%2C%20and%20it%20helps%20the%20C4%20optimize%20HDR%20content%20to%20better%20match%20the%20TV's%20specific%20capabilities.%20Without%20Dolby%20Vision%2C%20some%20HDR%20videos%20can%20look%20a%20bit%20blown%20out%20or%20dimmer%20than%20intended.%20Check%20out%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-hdr-tv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHDR%20guide%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20details.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bf763eea-0019-44df-aa3c-a74248f39d2d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Smart%20TV%20navigation%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELG's%20webOS%20isn't%20my%20favorite%20smart%20TV%20platform%2C%20but%20it%20works%20well%20enough%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20angled%20view%20of%20an%20LG%20C4%20OLED%20TV%20displaying%20its%20webOS%20homepage%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6827789b68a2929008019129%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221406%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELG's%20webOS%20system%20is%20decent%2C%20but%20it%20emphasizes%20sponsored%20content%20too%20much.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Muprhy%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20all%20LG%20TVs%2C%20the%20C4%20uses%20the%20brand's%20webOS%20smart%20TV%20interface.%20It's%20a%20decent%20enough%20platform%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20a%20huge%20fan%20for%20two%20key%20reasons%3A%20LG%20takes%20an%20%26quot%3Beverything%20and%20the%20kitchen%20sink%26quot%3B%20approach%20to%20features%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20a%20slog%20to%20navigate%20some%20of%20the%20menus%2C%20and%20LG%20still%20can't%20resist%20filling%20its%20homepage%20with%20unnecessary%20apps%2C%20recommendations%2C%20and%20advertising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELG%20isn't%20unique%20in%20those%20drawbacks%2C%20as%20plenty%20of%20streaming%20boxes%20and%20TVs%20are%20packed%20full%20of%20promos%20and%20ads%20nowadays.%20But%20other%20systems%20like%20Google%20TV%2C%20Roku%20OS%2C%20and%20Apple's%20tvOS%20are%20more%20intuitive.%20The%20TV's%20default%20settings%20present%20a%20big%20ad%20banner%20that%20takes%20up%20roughly%20one-third%20of%20the%20top%20of%20the%20C4's%20homepage.%20This%20ad%20can%20be%20disabled%20in%20the%20TV's%20menu%2C%20which%20is%20nice%2C%20but%20this%20function%20is%20buried%20several%20layers%20deep.%20You%20need%20to%20navigate%20to%20the%20C4's%20General%20Settings%2C%20then%20System%20Settings%2C%20then%20Additional%20Settings%2C%20and%20then%20finally%20Home%20Settings%20to%20see%20the%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20the%20top%20ad%20deactivated%2C%20the%20homepage%20is%20too%20focused%20on%20promos.%20Scrolling%20down%20below%20the%20top%20row%20of%20apps%20immediately%20presents%20you%20with%20screen-wide%20highlights%20for%20LG's%20%26quot%3Bfeatured%20channels.%26quot%3B%20After%20that%2C%20there's%20a%20row%20of%20boxes%20highlighting%20all%20the%20random%20stuff%20you%20can%20purchase%20via%20LG's%20integrated%20Shoptime%20app.%20The%20OS%20also%20lags%20a%20bit%20compared%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-streaming-devices%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20streaming%20devices%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20the%20Roku%20Ultra%20and%20Apple%20TV%204K.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20clear%2C%20even%20with%20those%20issues%2C%20webOS%20gets%20the%20job%20done.%20It%20supports%20all%20of%20the%20major%20streaming%20services%20you'll%20likely%20need%20and%20it%20does%20have%20a%20few%20handy%20features%20%E2%80%94%20including%20support%20for%20GeForce%20Now%20game%20streaming%2C%20a%20built-in%20smart%20home%20software%20hub%20for%20controlling%20connected%20IoT%20devices%20(which%20worked%20great%20with%20my%20Philips%20Hue%20lights%2C%20but%20not%20my%20TP-Link%20Tapo%20security%20cameras)%2C%20and%20fairly%20easy%20streaming%20from%20a%20Windows%20or%20Mac%20computer.%20I%20just%20wish%20LG%20would%20cut%20back%20on%20the%20promotions%20and%20optimize%20its%20organization%20a%20bit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22edabf96e-304c-4119-9b6e-ed451ac923c0%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Software%20bugs%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20temporary%20bug%20caused%20issues%20with%20the%20TV's%20software%2C%20but%20I%20found%20a%20fix%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20angled%20view%20of%20an%20LG%20C4%20OLED%20TV%20on%20a%20media%20console%20with%20the%20screen%20turned%20off.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682779533fe8d3928366190e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221406%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20TV's%20apps%20temporarily%20stopped%20working%20after%20a%20software%20update.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Murphy%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20to%20harp%20on%20webOS%20too%20much%2C%20but%20I%20also%20encountered%20a%20frustrating%20issue%20that%20temporarily%20made%20it%20impossible%20to%20use%20most%20of%20the%20TV's%20apps.%20Out%20of%20the%20box%2C%20the%20LG%20C4%20worked%20perfectly%3B%20I%20could%20install%20and%20launch%20streaming%20services%2C%20visit%20the%20various%20content%20hubs%2C%20and%20make%20ample%20use%20of%20the%20TV's%20voice%20recognition.%20As%20part%20of%20my%20regular%20use%2C%20I%20made%20sure%20to%20install%20any%20available%20software%20updates%2C%20and%20I%20set%20the%20TV%20to%20automatically%20download%20future%20updates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20some%20point%20during%20my%20month%20or%20so%20with%20the%20TV%2C%20one%20update%20went%20haywire.%20I%20couldn't%20access%20most%20of%20LG's%20apps%20or%20related%20content%2C%20or%20even%20use%20its%20voice%20assistant%2C%20without%20getting%20a%20%26quot%3Bcouldn't%20connect%26quot%3B%20error%20message.%20This%20sent%20me%20down%20the%20rabbit%20hole%20of%20troubleshooting%20my%20home%20network%20while%20scouring%20web%20forums%20for%20potential%20solutions.%20I%20finally%20found%20a%20workaround%3A%20switching%20the%20TV's%20location%20from%20the%20US%20to%20Canada%2C%20and%20then%20switching%20it%20back%2C%20which%20triggered%20the%20C4%20to%20make%20me%20re-sign%20its%20various%20user%20agreements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomehow%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20software%20update%2C%20the%20TV%20seemed%20to%20forget%20this%20critical%20part%20of%20the%20setup%20process%20that%20grants%20you%20full%20access%20to%20LG's%20apps%20and%20services.%20Several%20other%20users%20with%20different%20LG%20TVs%20seemed%20to%20be%20affected%20by%20similar%20errors%2C%20as%20evidenced%20by%20various%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FLGOLED%2Fcomments%2F1izi6if%2Fcant_update_apps_or_open_app_store%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReddit%20posts%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20haven't%20encountered%20this%20kind%20of%20service%20shutdown%20glitch%20on%20any%20other%20TV%20or%20streaming%20device%20I've%20reviewed%2C%20but%20since%20a%20fix%20was%20found%2C%20I%20don't%20consider%20it%20a%20dealbreaker.%20Likewise%2C%20fellow%20Insider%20Reviews%20testers%20who%20have%20covered%20other%20LG%20TV%20models%20have%20not%20run%20into%20this%20error.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223104f03a-b538-4587-8f8a-ca4b18616d5a%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Should%20you%20buy%20it%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShould%20you%20buy%20the%20LG%20C4%20OLED%204K%20TV%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221876%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20LG%20C4%20OLED%20TV%20displays%20a%20demo%20video%20of%20an%20emerald%20resting%20on%20a%20peacock%20feather.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682779acc6ad288d14812eef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221407%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20C4%20remains%20a%20great%20value%20for%20anyone%20who%20wants%20a%20midrange%20OLED%20TV.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Murphy%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELG's%20C4%20has%20great%20picture%20quality%20for%20its%20price%2C%20especially%20now%20that%20it's%20frequently%20discounted.%20The%20newer%20C5%20offers%20a%20few%20improvements%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20upgrade%20is%20worth%20the%20significant%20price%20jump%20for%20most%20people.%20For%20now%2C%20the%20C4%20remains%20a%20fantastic%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20direct%20competitors%2C%20Samsung's%20S90D%20OLED%20does%20have%20an%20edge%20when%20displaying%20especially%20bright%20colors%2C%20but%20only%20if%20you're%20looking%20at%20the%2055-%2C%2065-%2C%20or%2077-inch%20sizes.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20C4%20and%20S90D%20are%20neck%20and%20neck.%20Though%20the%20S90D%20remains%20the%20top%20pick%20in%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca