d%3C%2Fa%3E%20there%20was%20initially%20controversy%20around%20Donaldson's%20access%20to%20the%20sites.%20On%20Monday%2C%20the%20INAH%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inah.gob.mx%2Fboletines%2Fla-visita-del-youtuber-mr-beast-a-sitios-patrimoniales-se-realizo-en-apego-a-la-normatividad-del-inah%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20in%20a%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20necessary%20permits%20had%20been%20processed%20and%20that%20INAH%20personnel%20were%20supervising%20the%20recordings%20at%20all%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20INAH%20added%20that%20the%20video%20seemed%20to%20involve%20extensive%20post-production%20work%20and%20allude%20to%20events%20that%20never%20occurred%2C%20including%20a%20helicopter%20descent%20onto%20one%20of%20the%20temples%20and%20the%20handling%20of%20an%20ancient%20mask.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Sheinbaum%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyehQlFuc4cQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espoke%20publicly%20about%20the%20video%3C%2Fa%3E.%20CNN%20reported%20that%20she%20asked%20the%20INAH%20to%20report%20the%20conditions%20under%20which%20the%20production%20permit%20had%20been%20granted.%20If%20the%20permit%20was%20violated%2C%20she%20added%2C%20then%20sanctions%20must%20be%20determined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c12d0a51-a8f6-4852-b2fe-17eb7a78c645%5C%22%3E'It%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20this%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20political%20issue'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20the%20INAH%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FINAHmx%2Fstatus%2F1922873335009919291%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethread%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20was%20bringing%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20a%20production%20company%20called%20Full%20Circle%20Media%20that%20worked%20with%20Donaldson%20on%20the%20video.%20Donaldson%20himself%20isn't%20facing%20any%20legal%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thread%20alludes%20to%20a%20moment%20near%20the%20end%20of%20the%20video%2C%20when%20Donaldson%20is%20enjoying%20a%20traditional%20Mayan%20feast.%20After%20dinner%2C%20he%20brings%20out%20a%20box%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-says-cheaper-to-make-feastables-abroad-trump-tariffs-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFeastables%3C%2Fa%3E%20peanut%20butter%20cups%20for%20dessert%2C%20joking%20that%20it's%20the%20%26quot%3Bonly%20Mayan-approved%20snack%20on%20the%20planet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20INAH%20on%20X%20said%20that%20while%20it%20is%20open%20to%20collaboration%20to%20disseminate%20Mexico's%20cultural%20heritage%2C%20it%20condemned%20those%20who%20detract%20from%20the%20value%20of%20archaeological%20sites%20for%20commercial%20gain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20permit%20granted%20to%20Full%20Circle%20Media%20did%20not%20authorize%20the%20publication%20of%20false%20information%20or%20the%20use%20of%20the%20sites%20for%20advertising.%20The%20INAH%20is%20demanding%20compensation%20for%20damages%20and%20a%20public%20retraction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFull%20Circle%20Media%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20video%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20one%20of%20the%20pyramids%20in%20Egypt%2C%20was%20meant%20to%20highlight%20these%20%3Cspan%3Etreasured%20Mayan%20sites%20in%20Mexico%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20person%20close%20to%20MrBeast%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BNo%20advertisement%20material%20was%20shot%20on%20any%20archaeological%20sites%20overseen%20by%20INAH%20so%20it%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20this%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20political%20issue%20%E2%80%94%20hopefully%20it%20can%20lead%20to%20a%20productive%20dialogue%20and%20encourages%20people%20to%20visit%20these%20unique%20historical%20treasures.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmrbeast-mexico-controversy-explained-president-comments-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C